Role Description

This is a full-time on-site role for a Back End Developer at Sekeron Technologies Pvt. Ltd. located in New Delhi. The Back End Developer will be responsible for daily tasks related to back-end web development, software development, object-oriented programming (OOP), front-end development, and programming.


